#      did its job — anime corpus is excluded when filter=enterprise,
#      enterprise corpus is excluded when filter=anime).
#   2. The generator answers with a refusal phrase ("정보가 없습니다",
#      "문서에서 찾을 수 없습니다", etc.) rather than hallucinating
#      from the wrong-domain chunks that DID make it through.
#
# These rows are scored by run_eval rag --cross-domain (Phase 9 Section E).
